outputs.output_descr:
Outcome 1: strengthened institutional capacity of Gia Lai Forest Protection Department (FPD) in areas of forest management and protection, with specific emphasis on areas within and around the Kon Ka Kinh National Park and Kon Chu Rang Nature Reserve;

Outcome 2:  increased awareness among local communities, key decision-makers, scientific community and donors to the unique conservation values of the project area, building long-term support for forest management and protection throughout the project area; and

Outcome 3: established conditions for sustainable forest management and forest management certification in Dak Roong and Tram Lap State Forest Enterprises (SFEs), leading to the continued integrity of a forest corridor between Kon Ka Kinh National Park and Kon Chu Rang Nature Reserve
